h3(class="modal__content__heading modal__content__heading--path modal__content__heading__#{gameNumber}")=description
p.modal__content__subheading--path 
	| Click on the blocks to select and begin your path. Hint, start at start. 

.path-shadow
div(class="path__challenge path-challenge__#{gameNumber}")
	h6.position.position-start start
	h6.position.position-finish finish
	table.path-challenge__table
		each row in grid
			tr.path-challenge__grid-items
				each column in row
					td.path-challenge__grid-item.path-challenge__grid-item--play=column

	.action-btns
		button.btn.btn--reset 
			| Reset &raquo;
		button(disabled="disabled").btn.btn--submit 
			| Submit #{gameNumber} / 3 &raquo;